px; word-wrap: break-word;\">2018年01月最新报价制表</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); position: relative; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal;\">外观方面，奔驰G63AMG基于改款<a class=\"t_link\" href=\"http://product.cheshi.com/bseries_601/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(102, 102, 102); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">奔驰G级</span></a>打造，与普通版<a class=\"t_link\" href=\"http://product.cheshi.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(102, 102, 102); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">车型</span></a>相比，外观采用了大尺寸前保险杠、全套车身动力学套件、还配备了镀铬中网和V12 BITURBO标识彰显这款车的身份。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); position: relative; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"17款奔驰G63AMG加版 有钱人的奢华大玩具-图2\" src=\"http://image.bitautoimg.com/appimage/media/20180115/w600_h800_670158df700b41daa2050f2957ffcb0c.jpeg\" data-original=\"http://image.bitautoimg.com/appimage/media/20180115/w600_h800_670158df700b41daa2050f2957ffcb0c.jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border-width: initial; border-style: none; max-width: 614px; overflow: hidden;\"/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); position: relative; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"17款奔驰G63AMG加版 有钱人的奢华大玩具-图3\" src=\"http://image.bitautoimg.com/appimage/media/20180115/w600_h450_cec7b14684264b4bad3e754f76f3d483.jpeg\" data-original=\"http://image.bitautoimg.com/appimage/media/20180115/w600_h450_cec7b14684264b4bad3e754f76f3d483.jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; border-width: initial; border-style: none; max-width: 614px; overflow: hidde