><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">去世时间</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">756年7月15日</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">主要成就</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">后世评价为<a class=\"ed_inner_link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.sogou.com/v800228.htm\" ss_c=\"ssc.citiao.link\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">中国古代四大美女</a>之一</td></tr></tbody></table></td><td class=\"abstract_list_wrap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 320px; vertical-align: top;\"><table class=\"abstract_list\" style=\"width: 304px;\"><tbody><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">别&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;称</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">杨太真、<a class=\"ed_inner_link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.sogou.com/v148583466.htm\" ss_c=\"ssc.citiao.link\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">杨玉</a>、杨贵妃、玉奴</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">所处时代</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">唐朝</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">出生时间</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">719年6月22日</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">主要作品</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">《<a class=\"ed_inner_link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.sogou.com/v71624753.htm\" ss_c=\"ssc.citiao.link\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">赠张云容舞</a>》</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">职&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;业</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\"><a class=\"ed_inner_link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.sogou.com/v100116305.htm\" ss_c=\"ssc.citiao.link\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">寿王妃</a>→道士→贵妃→舞蹈家</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div id=\"j-big-image-scroll-wrap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></div></div><div id=\"j-tab-module-wrap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, &quot;pingfang sc&quot;, stheiti, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"content_nav_box column_04\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 20px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, &quot;pingfang sc&quot;, stheiti, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; width: 710px; background: rgb