 border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">西施、西子</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">民 族</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">华夏族</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">出生日期</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">7月19日（六月初三）</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">主要成就</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">忍辱负重、以身报国、灭吴</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">相关成语</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">西子捧心、闭月羞花、沉鱼落雁</td></tr><tr><th style=\"margin: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 700; width: 90px; line-height: 27px; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(222, 223, 225); vertical-align: top;\">丈 夫</th><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 27px; border-top-style: dashed; border-top-color: rgb(222, 223, 225); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all;\">吴王夫差</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div id=\"j-big-image-scro